{"tid":1593961,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[黑手套]與李小加出席同一論壇  倫交所CEO：上海才是中國金融中心","createTime":"2019-09-25T10:12:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-26T02:37:05.000Z","uid":41818,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b21c346718ffe531f5aa5d0d3dedd4a5d11a65a5","tid":1593961,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T10:12:35.000Z","msg":"倫交所行政總裁David Schwimmer與港交所行政總裁李小加，日前出席倫敦的SIBOS論壇，外電報道，Schwimmer在論壇上表示，雖然香港在全球金融市場定位強勁，惟長遠而言，上海才是中國的金融中心。<br />\n<br />\n李小加在倫敦同一論壇表示，由於中國銀行體系當中有27萬億美元的資金需作出配置，目前是創立一個全球交易所的時機。<br />\n<br />\n李小加和Schwimmer均表示，中國不會急於放寬資本管制，惟Schwimmer稱這是無可避免的事情，李小加認為中國放寬資本管制需時20年或以上時間達成。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.aastocks.com/tc/stocks/news/aafn-con/NOW.967332/popular-news\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.aastocks.com%2Ftc%2Fstocks%2Fnews%2Faafn-con%2FNOW.967332%2Fpopular-news&d=ZBayvnjX3omFcj6xyood9LTKTGNgLIIXgyzGYx6bzTs%3D&h=ae850358\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.aastocks.com/tc/stocks/news/aafn-con/NOW.967332/popular-news</a>"},{"pid":"594cd7dfdf81e4337ffa251e809108f0bdd26b57","tid":1593961,"uid":72633,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T10:18:01.000Z","msg":"姐係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n英國仲想繼續食中國條水？"},{"pid":"ff3f843b01d4727a85123885441eed8c641f2858","tid":1593961,"uid":141793,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"594cd7dfdf81e4337ffa251e809108f0bdd26b57","tid":1593961,"uid":72633,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T10:18:01.000Z","msg":"姐係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n英國仲想繼續食中國條水？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T10:20:04.000Z","msg":"梗架喇<br />\n唔係撞正中美貿易戰 同 美帝發現中國威脅勃起 都唔會理香港"},{"pid":"9ae5a290614ddea98a1c79295f710c181cf41666","tid":1593961,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T10:23:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">Brexit都係靠呢招食糊！</span><br />\n 【眾籌 Y